Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cum ți se pare noul nostru parfeu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,, Este dulce, rece și absolut delicios!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ui-chan, asta spui mereu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Înghețata mea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doamne, la naiba cu Daigo...
Dialogue: 4,0:02:18.70,0:02:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă cheamă până în Honchou...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...și apoi îmi face un tur al magazinelor de adulți? Pe bune?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakai-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce s-a întâmplat? De ce stai aici de una singură?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai febră?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...presupun că nu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci... ce este?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi este... foame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presupun că toți mănâncă așa când le este cu adevărat foame. Chiar și tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu mă înțelege greșit. De fapt, cred că este un lucru bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îți plac fetele care mănâncă mult?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Păi, ei bine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oricum, cum ai sfârșit astfel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Știi, aproape leșinasei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am fugit de acasă.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fugit de acasă?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să fugi de acasă înseamnă să pleci fără permisiunea părinților sau protectorilor tăi, fără vreo intenție de reîntoarcere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Știu ce înseamnă!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-am certat cu tatăl meu și am fugit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu mi-am luat portofelul, haine de schimb... nimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci ce plănuiești să faci?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Nu-mi arăta acei ochi de cățeluș!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pe lângă asta, pentru început sunt lăsat doar să stau la Yorozuyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mersi pentru pâine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă voi descurca cu restul singură.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt acasă...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci asta este camera ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este mică, dar te rog să te simți \Nliberă să stai aici pentru o perioadă.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, tavanul este mai jos acolo, deci ai gri{\fscx350}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, te-ai întors deja?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Da, m-am întors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nee-san spune că este timpul pentru cină.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine, am înțeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu vii?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trebuie să mă ocup de niște lucruri...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spune-i lui Nee-san că voi fi acolo imediat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai, cum rămâne cu cina?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am mâncat mult acolo, deci voi fi în regulă pentru astăzi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, voi merge să mănânc, deci așteaptă puțin doar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(645.714,769.286)}{semn}Șervețele Umede
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai, scuze că te-am făcut să aștep{\fscx350}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuma-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce este în neregulă? Am auzit un țipăt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-O viepse a intrat în camera mea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Viespii sunt diurni.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu sunt văzuți de obicei{\fscx350}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta chiar nu contează acum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuma-kun, ești bine acolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sunt bine! A zburat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Ce naiba făceai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eram transpirată, deci voiam să mă șterg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci ar fi trebuit să-mi spui.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ți-aș fi adus un prosop ud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este în regulă acum. M-am îmbrăcat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu mă surprinde așa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă te găsește Nee-san{\fscx350}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am uitat să mi-l pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acesta este paradisul...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să faci o baie lungă după o zi de muncă este cel mai bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, Senpai, poți dormi aici astă-seară.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cum rămâne cu tine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu voi dormi pe podea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu te pot lăsa să faci asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sunt oaspetele aici. Eu voi dormi pe podea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar nu pot lăsa o fată să doarmă \Npe podea în timp eu dorm în pat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci haide să facem astfel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Putem dormi amândoi așa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar asta este puțin, știi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-ți face griji, nu mă mișc în somn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu, dar totuși...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu te voi lovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai, de ce te-ai certat cu tatăl tău?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, este în regulă dacă nu vrei să-mi spui.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vreau să merg la o universitate în Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deși, tatăl meu este împotrivă.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,El crede că nu mă voi întoarce dacă merg în Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doar mirosului sakeului mă face să mă simt amețită, deci îmi este imposibil să-l fac.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar pot ajuta la vânzarea lui.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De asta vreau să merg la un colegiu și să studiez \Nmarketingul, crearea produselor și lucruri de genul acesta...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:09:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și apoi vreau să prezint sakeul nostru la mulți oameni în foarte multe feluri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai, i-ai spus asta tatălui tău?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am încercat de multe ori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prima oară, a început să țipe la mine cum am menționat mersul la o universitate în Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apoi, mama și tata au început să se certe când am încercat să le spun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apoi, tata a țipat la mine din nou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apoi, ne-am certat din nou când eram la jumătate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apoi, venise un client când am încercat să-i spun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apoi, eram la jumătate când{\fscx350}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este în regulă, înțeleg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci nu i-ai spus încă.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă simt de parcă nu voi reuși s-o fac tot restul vieții.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu este adevărat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odată ce găsești oportunitatea perfectă{\fscx350}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, așa este.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce este?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi cer scuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide, este în regulă.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trebuie să ne ajutăm reciproc când avem probleme{\fscx350}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu, nu la asta mă refeream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Când ne-am întâlnit pentru prima oară...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai spus că brelocul meu de telefon era drăguț, \Ndar eu am înțeles greșit și m-am enervat pe tine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(250,200)}Nu face mișto de mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am vrut să-mi cer scuze în tot acest timp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar nu am reușit până acum și chiar mă deranja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vezi, tocmai mi-ai spus ceva ce \Nnu ai reușit s-o faci până acum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt sigur că vei reuși să faci \Nla fel și cu tatăl tău într-o zi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce este?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mersi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuma-kun, chiar ar trebui să te trezești.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu poți dormi pentru totdeauna \Ndoar pentru că este vacanța de vară.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuma-kun, te-ai trezit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Intru să-ți iau salteaua.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Așteaptă puțin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg situația.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-mi place faptul că nu ai vorbit cu mine mai întâi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dar când o pasăre încolțită zboară \Nîn drumul vânătorului, acesta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,acesta... acesta... va fi surprins?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Când o pasăre încolțită zboară în drumul vânătorului, acesta nu o va împușca.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta voiam să spun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acum că am spus asta, ca proprietară a Hanului Yorozuyo, nu te pot ignora pur și simplu când ai probleme.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oricum, cine nu muncește, nu mănâncă.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cât timp stai aici, te voi pune să ajuți ca stagiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ne-am înțeles?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arată destul de bine pe tine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De ce trebuie și {\i1}eu{\i0} să fac asta mai exact?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi-san este într-o vacanță cu familia de ieri. Aveam doar nevoie de câțeva persoane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, contez pe voi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine ați{\fscx350}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tată!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hina!  Deci este adevărat că lucrai \Ncu jumătate de normă la Yorozuyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presupun că voi face curat la intrare acum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nee-san chiar este o exploatatoare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.09,Dialogue Overlap,,0,0,0,,Nu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu vreau!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am spus să vii cu mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, oprește-te!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cine naiba ești?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cine ești {\i1}tu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Încetează, tată.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tată?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci ești{\fscx350}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu ești acel copil de la oraș...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg. Tu ești cel care o pune să facă asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu, Hoshino nu are nimic de a face cu asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taci! Am spus să nu te bagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să tacă?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ea nu reușește să spună nimic \Ndeoarece continuați să țipați la ea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Încerci să spui ceva legat de mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai încearcă să intre la colegiu \Nca să vă poate ajuta cu munca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wants to let even more people know about the sake her family makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why she wants to study all kinds of related subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este adevărat, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci de ce nu mi-ai spus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pentru că nu ați lăsat-o să spună nimic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taci! Nu te băga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu vreau!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brat, acting all cocky just because you came from the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakai-san, I ask you not to be violent on Yorozuyo grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kid was getting in my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm still taking my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuma-kun is one of the important guests we're currently housing at this inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your daughter is here under his care,\Nand therefore also a guest of Yorozuyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the Heavens flip upside down, I'm not letting anyone take our guests by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a call from the owner of Yorozuyo earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said they're taking good care of our daughter, so we shouldn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop pretending you're asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, I knew you were awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You moron! Anyone would wake up from that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She also told me why Hina wants to continue her studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wants to help the family business, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it was worth the pain, knowing she grew up to be a good child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not only your kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't understand how you want to keep your cute daughter close to home,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you should try considering her feelings a little too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai's father challenged me to a duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just a tug-of-war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tug-of-war?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cultural activity in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To settle a dispute between two villages,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,people would hold a tug-of-war duel between the strongest men of both villages at the Kotama Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until my grandmother's generation,\Ntwo men would often have a duel over a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never thought someone would do it in this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why is he challenging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he thinks you're some kind of bad bug influencing his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bad bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hoshino, you don't have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to cause you any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make that old fart cry like a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Kazuma-kun wins, we'll do whatever we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Sakai-san wins, we'll quietly hand her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, do I really have to wear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is{\i0} a shrine ceremony, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to wear the customary clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, why did so many people come to watch{\fscx350}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.68,Dialogue Overlap,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumu, why are {\i1}you{\i0} wearing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Nee-san said that if I'm seriously going to cheer you on, I should be wearing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen well! This is a sacred match in front of a shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it everything you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young boys sure have nice rears!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so smooth, I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we could trade it with my husband's dirty one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.13,Dialogue Overlap,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard this is a sacred match!\NStop watching it for the wrong reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, both sides shall grab the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, put some muscle into it, Sakai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you lose to that squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's starting to even out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, make your dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Match set! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... This is, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have our meal, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father's been in a bad mood ever since he lost the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't even come out of his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he still hasn't forgiven me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was planning on challenging Hoshino and losing on purpose in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he wanted to play the father who supports his daughter from behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he got serious during the match,\Nran out of stamina, and ended up the way he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just annoyed because it didn't go as he planned, and it didn't make him look good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heh, maybe it's his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back in the day, he could go for many rounds, though he was pretty fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot, don't make fun of your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're cute when you're embarrassed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.58,0:23:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumu-kun, it's about time for the preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll do it in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, Hoshizora e Kakaru Hashi, Episode Ten:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Ring Drifted Away, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.46,0:24:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dragonfly, it's a dragonfly...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dragonfly, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.72,0:24:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of dream he's having.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now it's a rat snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rat snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cobra! It's Onii-chan's king cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumu-kun, fugi!
